      "content": "Feel your pain so deeply it feels like relief, yet remember that shadows cannot truly take you without you choosing to stay. Every sunrise, however hollow the world feels, offers a tiny, cruel gift of a reason to try again. Even in ash, there was once sparks that prove your heart mattered then and could matter again.",
